Run shell commands via exec_command before any final answer. For edits, read ~/.config/karabiner.edn first, make a minimal targeted change, run goku, then verify the generated Karabiner JSON.

## Command map
show config / inspect mappings -> sed -n '1,240p' ~/.config/karabiner.edn
compile / check config -> goku
verify generated json -> grep -n "EXPECTED_TEXT" ~/.config/karabiner/karabiner.json
